  06 Jul 2014; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> tox-1.4.3-r1.ebuild,
  tox-1.4.3.ebuild, tox-1.7.1.ebuild:
  Clean up obsolete dependencies on virtual/python-argparse and virtual/python-
  unittest2 (those packages were only required for <=python-2.6).

  23 Jun 2014; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> -tox-1.6.1.ebuild,
  -tox-1.7.0.ebuild:
  Remove old.

